data.description: Step into this charming home with many new updates! The kitchen has been remodeled and all new light fixtures throughout this lovely home! New paint, gutters, and shutters are just a few of the new updates. This huge corner lot is completely fenced in and has a separate detached garage and a delightful pergola to sit under and enjoy this wonderful outdoor space! Call and schedule your private showing today!
